				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Juárez, Mexico" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Ju%C3%A1rez_(disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect mw-disambig" title="Juárez (disambiguation)">Juárez (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
